316
00:14:07,825 --> 00:14:08,702
Com licen...

317
00:14:09,170 --> 00:14:10,177
O que está acontecendo?

318
00:14:10,860 --> 00:14:11,674
O que foi...?

319
00:14:11,847 --> 00:14:12,828
Desculpe...

320
00:14:12,829 --> 00:14:14,596
Qual...Qual...é
o problema?

321
00:14:17,554 --> 00:14:18,518
Venha aqui.

322
00:14:19,075 --> 00:14:21,076
Apenas...apenas...
apenas...apenas...

323
00:14:25,570 --> 00:14:26,792
